Powered by RubiQube Ad Network Yobe State Governor, Mala Buni, has taken Ibrahim Gaidam’s daughter Ummi Adama Gaidam as his third wife. The low-key wedding fathia held on Thursday at the residence of the immediate past governor of the state in Sabon Fegi area of Damaturu, the state capital. Islamic scholar, Sheik Abubakar Adam who is an associate of both Gaidam and Buni gave out the bride. Sheik Adam, who officiated the wedding called on the couple to fear God in all their dealings in order to have a good family and live a fulfilling life. The marriage which took place barely 24hours after the governor’s swearing in ceremony has been tagged a matrimony to strengthen the political relationship between Governor Buni and Gaidam.